subject: VPD-Tool: PowerSupply Collection
commitMessage:
VPD-Tool: PowerSupply Collection

Vpd tool now collects power supply fru data as well.

In response to the below commit:
< https://gerrit.openbmc-project.xyz/c/openbmc/openpower-vpd-parser/+/35140 >
Fixed the issues.

Signed-off-by: Priyanga Ramasamy <priyanga24@in.ibm.com>
Change-Id: I5f1fe6ba2fdf4883715675bc3349cee68bf914eb
